Project Structure MHMA (Initial Setup)

mood-journal-geeta/
│
├── app.py                    ← Flask backend
├── templates/
│   └── index.html            ← Journal input page
├── static/
│   ├── style.css             ← Styling
│   └── script.js             ← Optional JS for frontend
├── mood_detector.py         ← NLP sentiment analysis logic
├── geeta_mapping.py         ← Map mood to Geeta shloks
├── database.sql             ← SQL file to set up the database
├── mood_wheel.html          ← Optional spin wheel page
└── requirements.txt         ← List of Python packages
